Apollo Investment Corporation
















 


























Apollo Investment Corporation is a publicly-traded closed-end management investment company.




We provide private middle-market companies with an alternative to traditional financing sources.




Our portfolio consists primarily of subordinated and senior secured debt.




Find information about Apollo Investment Corporation's latest investments, performance, portfolio and outlook.




Apollo Investment Corporation (NASDAQ: AINV), managed by Apollo Investment Management, provides investors access to attractive opportunities in privately-held, middle-market companies. 







© 2017 Apollo Investment Corporation (AINV). All rights reserved.









Apollo Global Management - Wikipedia






















 







Apollo Global Management

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Apollo Global Management, LLC





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: APO


Industry
